<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="starve-v">starve <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stɑːv/    美 /stɑːrv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 挨饿；饿死：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>starve to death</strong>
饿死</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’s <strong>starving herself</strong> trying to lose weight.
她为了减肥而挨饿。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-starving">be starving</h3>
<p>1.<strong>饿极了：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When’s food? I’m starving!
饭什么时候好？我快饿死了！</p></div></div>